===Etymology===
{{Han compound|火|商|c1=s|c2=p|t1=fire|t2=quotient|ls=psc}}

First produced by Chinese physical scientist Hu Gangfu ([[w:zh:胡剛復|胡剛復]]) in 1923 to traslate the concept of [[entropy]] in thermodynamics, where 商 ([[quotient]]) means the quotient of [[heat]] and [[temperature]], and 火 (fire) means it is relavent to the [[thermodynamics]].

